<h1>About CommunEdy</h1>
<p>CommunEdy is a resource and network designed by a former teacher to help other teachers. Teaching is so important, but it can be challenging! A supportive community and resources can help prevent burnout and allow you to use your time efficiently, both inside and outside of the classroom. On CommunEdy, you can to share and receive unit and lesson plans, activity and assessment ideas, feedback on teaching or planning, advice, and support. Find out about relevant education technology to help you in the difficult work you do. Network to find out about new ideas to help you be creative in the classroom, as well as learn about new opportunities. New teachers, find support to navigate the first few years successfully; experienced teachers, share your knowledge with others as mentors. Join our CommunEdy today! </p>
